of the best RPers ever. Better than you. Rdahl, i owned Soundwave.  He died a

Vulois. He failed, but he will always be a hero. If you bring him back, do 
you agree to have him join Vulois' group?

:::Vulois/Starscream:::

::Vulois and Starscream all of a sudden feel a pain deep down in their 
sparks. That is because part of it is gone::
